Hatchery.Description:
Primary structure. Used to spawn all Zerg units and receive gathered resources. Grows creep used to feed nearby Zerg structures. Can mutate into a Lair.

Bonus: Zerg move faster on creep.
Hatchery.Name: Hatchery

Lair.Description:
Evolved version of the Hatchery that allows additional upgrades and structures to be produced. Also spawns all Zerg units and receives gathered resources.

Enables:
- Overseers from Overlords
Lair.Name: Lair

Hive.Description:
Further evolved version of the Hatchery that allows additional upgrades and structures to be produced. Also spawns all Zerg units and receives gathered resources.

Enables:
- Vipers from Larvae
Hive.Name: Hive

Queen.Description: Defensive unit. Can use Spawn Larvae, Spawn Creep Tumor, and Transfusion. Moves much faster on creep.**Can attack ground and air units**
Queen.Name: Queen

QueenBurrowed.Description: Defensive unit. Can use Spawn Larvae, Spawn Creep Tumor, and Transfusion. Moves much faster on creep.**Can attack ground and air units**
QueenBurrowed.Name: Queen

Egg.Description: Zerg units morph in the safety of these cocoons.
Egg.Name: Zerg Cocoon

Drone.Description:
Basic worker unit. Can harvest minerals and vespene gas. Can mutate into structures.

Can attack ground units.
Drone.Name: Drone

DroneBurrowed.Description:
Basic worker unit. Can harvest minerals and vespene gas. Can mutate into structures.

Can attack ground units.
DroneBurrowed.Name: Drone

Extractor.Description: Mutated over a Vespene Geyser to allow harvesting of vespene gas.
Extractor.Name: Extractor

SpawningPool.Description:
Contains upgrades for Zerglings.

Enables:
- Queens at the Hatchery, Lair, or Hive
- Zerglings from Larvae
- Spine Crawlers from Drones
- Spore Crawlers from Drones
SpawningPool.Name: Spawning Pool

EvolutionChamber.Description: Contains upgrades for Zerg ground units.
EvolutionChamber.Name: Evolution Chamber

BanelingNest.Description:
Contains an upgrade for Banelings.

Enables:
- Banelings from Zerglings
BanelingNest.Name: Baneling Nest

RoachWarren.Description:
Contains upgrades for Roaches.

Enables:
- Roaches from Larvae
- Ravagers from Roaches
RoachWarren.Name: Roach Warren

SpineCrawler.Description: Anti-ground defensive structure. **Can attack ground units**
SpineCrawler.Name: Spine Crawler

SpineCrawlerUprooted.Description: Uprooted anti-ground defensive structure. Can move when uprooted, but cannot attack. Must plant itself in creep to attack.
SpineCrawlerUprooted.Name: Spine Crawler

SporeCrawler.Description:
Anti-air defensive structure. **Can attack air units**
Detector
SporeCrawler.Name: Spore Crawler

SporeCrawlerUprooted.Description: Uprooted anti-air defensive structure. Can move when uprooted, but cannot attack. Must plant itself in creep to attack.
SporeCrawlerUprooted.Name: Spore Crawler

Spire.Description:
Contains upgrades for Zerg air units. Can mutate into a Greater Spire.

Enables:
- Mutalisks from Larvae
- Corruptors from Larvae
Spire.Name: Spire

GreaterSpire.Description:
Contains upgrades for Zerg air units.

Enables:
- Brood Lords from Corruptors
GreaterSpire.Name: Greater Spire

UltraliskCavern.Description:
Contains an upgrade for Ultralisks.

Enables:
- Ultralisks from Larvae
UltraliskCavern.Name: Ultralisk Cavern

NydusNetwork.Description:
Friendly ground units can use the Nydus Network to instantly travel to any other Nydus Network or Nydus Worm owned by the player.

Enables:
- Nydus Worm
NydusNetwork.Name: Nydus Network

NydusCanal.Description:
Friendly ground units can use a Nydus Worm to instantly travel to any other Nydus Worm or Nydus Network owned by the player. Grows creep used to feed nearby Zerg structures.

Bonus: Zerg move faster on creep.
NydusCanal.Name: Nydus Worm

InfestationPit.Description:
Contains upgrades for Infestors and Swarm Hosts.

Enables:
- Infestors from Larvae
- Swarm Hosts from Larvae
InfestationPit.Name: Infestation Pit

HydraliskDen.Description:
Contains an upgrade for Hydralisks. Can mutate into a Lurker Den.

Enables:
- Hydralisks from Larvae
HydraliskDen.Name: Hydralisk Den

LurkerDenMP.Description:
Contains an upgrade for Lurkers.

Enables:
- Lurkers from Hydralisks
LurkerDenMP.Name: Lurker Den

Zergling.Description: Fast melee creature. Can morph into a Baneling.**Can attack ground units**
Zergling.Name: Zergling

BanelingCocoon.Description: This cocoon contains a Zergling that is morphing into a Baneling.
BanelingCocoon.Name: Baneling Cocoon

Baneling.Description: Suicide unit. Does damage over a small area on death. **Can attack ground units**
Baneling.Name: Baneling

BanelingBurrowed.Description: Suicide unit. Does damage over a small area on death. **Can attack ground units**
BanelingBurrowed.Name: Baneling

ZerglingBurrowed.Description: Fast melee creature. Can morph into a Baneling.**Can attack ground units**
ZerglingBurrowed.Name: Zergling

Overlord.Description:
Provides supply.
Supply allows you to create more units.
Overlord.Name: Overlord

OverlordCocoon.Description: This cocoon contains an Overlord as it is morphing into an Overseer.
OverlordCocoon.Name: Overseer Cocoon

Overseer.Description:
Advanced aerial observer. Maintains the unit cap set by the Overlord. Can use the Spawn Changeling and Contaminate abilities.

Detector
Overseer.Name: Overseer

OverseerSiegeMode.Description:
Advanced aerial observer. Maintains the unit cap set by the Overlord. Can use the Spawn Changeling and Contaminate abilities.

Detector
OverseerSiegeMode.Name: Overseer

Changeling.Description: Changelings cannot attack. When a Changeling first encounters an enemy unit, it will match that unit's color and change into a Zealot, Marine, or Zergling, depending on the enemy race. Dies after 150.
Changeling.Name: Changeling

OverlordTransport.Description:
Provides supply.
Supply allows you to create more units.
OverlordTransport.Name: Overlord

Roach.Description: Assault unit. Regenerates life quickly when burrowed. Can morph into a Ravager.**Can attack ground units**
Roach.Name: Roach

RoachBurrowed.Description: Assault unit. Regenerates life quickly when burrowed. Can morph into a Ravager.**Can attack ground units**
RoachBurrowed.Name: Roach

RavagerCocoon.Description: This cocoon contains a Roach that is morphing into a Ravager.
RavagerCocoon.Name: Ravager Cocoon

Ravager.Description:
Ranged artillery. Can use Corrosive Bile.

Can attack ground units.
Ravager.Name: Ravager

RavagerBurrowed.Description:
Ranged artillery. Can use Corrosive Bile.

Can attack ground units.
RavagerBurrowed.Name: Ravager

Mutalisk.Description: Air unit. Bounces its shot to strike multiple targets.**Can attack ground and air units**
Mutalisk.Name: Mutalisk

Infestor.Description: Infestation specialist. Can use the Fungal Growth, Infested Terran, and Neural Parasite abilities.
Infestor.Name: Infestor

InfestorBurrowed.Description: Infestation specialist. Can use the Fungal Growth, Infested Terran, and Neural Parasite abilities.
InfestorBurrowed.Name: Infestor

Ultralisk.Description: Heavy assault beast. Has an area-damage attack.**Can attack ground units**
Ultralisk.Name: Ultralisk

UltraliskBurrowed.Description: Heavy assault beast. Has an area-damage attack.**Can attack ground units**
UltraliskBurrowed.Name: Ultralisk

Corruptor.Description:
Anti-air flyer. Can use Caustic Spray. Can morph into a Brood Lord.

Can attack air units.
Corruptor.Name: Corruptor

BroodLordCocoon.Description: This cocoon contains a Corruptor that is morphing into a Brood Lord.
BroodLordCocoon.Name: Brood Lord Cocoon

BroodLord.Description:
Flying heavy-assault unit. Shoots Broodlings at its target. A Broodling is a small creature that can attack ground units.

Can attack ground units.
BroodLord.Name: Brood Lord

Hydralisk.Description: Ranged attacker. Can morph into a Lurker.**Can attack ground and air units**
Hydralisk.Name: Hydralisk

HydraliskBurrowed.Description: Ranged attacker. Can morph into a Lurker.**Can attack ground and air units**
HydraliskBurrowed.Name: Hydralisk

LurkerMPEgg.Description: This cocoon contains a Hydralisk that is morphing into a Lurker.
LurkerMPEgg.Name: Lurker Cocoon

LurkerMP.Description:
Anti-ground ambusher. Has a spine attack that damages all enemy units in its line of fire.

Can attack ground units.
Must burrow to attack.
LurkerMP.Name: Lurker

LurkerMPBurrowed.Description:
Anti-ground ambusher. Has a spine attack that damages all enemy units in its line of fire.

Can attack ground units.
Must burrow to attack.
LurkerMPBurrowed.Name: Lurker

Viper.Description: Flying caster. Able to manipulate battlefield conditions. Can use Parasitic Bomb, Consume, Blinding Cloud, and Abduct abilities.
Viper.Name: Viper

SwarmHostMP.Description:
Siege unit that attacks while burrowed by spawning Locust minions.

Locusts can attack ground units.
SwarmHostMP.Name: Swarm Host

SwarmHostBurrowedMP.Description:
Siege unit that attacks while burrowed by spawning Locust minions.

Locusts can attack ground units.
SwarmHostBurrowedMP.Name: Swarm Host

LocustMP.Description:
Timed life creature. Durable and dangerous.

Can attack ground units.
LocustMP.Name: Locust
